data.description: Discover the epitome of East Beach elegance at this condo. At the heart of this unit is a gas fireplace, a statement piece that not only warms the space but also serves as a gathering point for cozy evenings. The primary bedroom is a spacious sanctuary, offering ample room to retreat and rejuvenate.  Step out onto the beautiful deck and let the fresh bay breezes envelop you, a spot perfect for savoring your morning espresso or toasting the twilight with a glass of wine as the stars begin their nightly dance.  Life at Bay Point extends beyond the walls of your condo. Here, a sense of community thrives amidst the luxury amenities. A clubhouse that's both welcoming and well-appointed, a shimmering pool that beckons for a refreshing dip, and tennis courts that await your winning serve. All of this set within the vibrant pulse of East Beach.
